                If your merchants are moving to integrated payments, but not all at once, you need an integrated-ready terminal.
                Give your merchants standalone mobile payments today.  When they switch to using a POS integrated with Handpoint, 
                a click of the mouse in your cloud-hosted platform switches the terminal to integrated.  No costs for reterminalization.
                No delays for key injections.
